The 6.4.2 release of devel/py-setuptools has been committed recently which has textproc/py-tomli as a fixed dependency. The reported issue and other issues with ports that require "setuptools_scm[toml]" should be fixed.

I'll leave this bug open for a few days for reference.

@koobs: If you like you can assign the bug over to me and I'll close it.
